	<li class="cat-item cat-item-17074"><a href="https://www.slrlounge.com/photography/basics/" title="The Photography basics category of our site will give you a foundation for your photography education. While many of these are considered beginner or 101 tips and tutorials, they are essential to your understanding of photography.">Photography Basics</a>
